<li>remembering privacy and security settings</li>
<li>analysing site traffic and usage</li>
<li>personalized search, content, and recommendations</li>
<li>helping sellers understand their audience</li>
<li>showing relevant, targeted ads on and off Etsy</li>
</ul>
<p class="wt-text-caption wt-line-height-tight wt-text-link">Detailed information can be found in Etsy’s <a class="wt-text-link" href="https://www.etsy.com/legal/cookies-and-tracking-technologies">Cookies &amp; Similar Technologies Policy</a> and our <a class="wt-text-link" href="https://www.etsy.com/legal/privacy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="wt-pt-xl-6 wt-display-flex-xl wt-pt-lg-6 wt-display-flex-lg wt-pt-md-6 wt-display-flex-md wt-pt-sm-6 wt-display-flex-sm wt-pt-xs-6 wt-display-flex-xs" data-section="cookies">
        <div class="wt-flex-xl-5 wt-flex-lg-5 wt-flex-md-5 wt-flex-sm-5 wt-flex-xs-5">
            <h2 class="wt-text-title-01 wt-mb-xs-4 wt-break-word">Required Cookies &amp; Technologies</h2>
<p class="wt-text-caption wt-mb-xs-2">Some of the technologies we use are necessary for critical functions like security and site integrity, account authentication, security and privacy preferences, internal site usage and maintenance data, and to make the site work correctly for browsing and transactions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="wt-position-right">
            <div class="wt-text-caption">Always on</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wt-pt-xl-6 wt-display-flex-xl wt-pt-lg-6 wt-display-flex-lg wt-pt-md-6 wt-display-flex-md wt-pt-sm-6 wt-display-flex-sm wt-pt-xs-6 wt-display-flex-xs" data-section="personalization_consent">
        <div class="wt-flex-xl-5 wt-flex-lg-5 wt-flex-md-5 wt-flex-sm-5 wt-flex-xs-5">
            <h2 class="wt-text-title-01 wt-mb-xs-4">Site Customization</h2>
<p class="wt-text-caption wt-max-width-sm">Cookies and similar technologies are used to improve your experience, to do things like:</p>
<ul class="wt-text-caption wt-ml-xs-2 wt-mb-xs-2 wt-mt-xs-2 wt-max-width-sm">
<li>remember your login, general, and regional preferences</li>
<li>personalize content, search, recommendations, and offers</li>
</ul>
<p class="wt-text-caption wt-line-height-tight wt-text-link">Without these technologies, things like personalized recommendations, your account preferences, or localisation may not work correctly. Find out more in our <a class="wt-text-link" href="https://www.etsy.com/legal/cookies-and-tracking-technologies">Cookies &amp; Similar Technologies Policy.</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="wt-flex-xl-1 wt-flex-lg-1 wt-flex-md-1 wt-flex-sm-1 wt-flex-xs-1">
            <div class="wt-display-flex-xl wt-display-flex-lg wt-display-flex-md wt-display-flex-sm wt-display-flex-xs wt-nudge-b-4">
                <label for="personalization_consent" class="wt-text-caption wt-pt-xl-1 wt-pr-xl-2 wt-pt-lg-1 wt-pr-lg-2 wt-pt-md-1 wt-pr-md-2 wt-pt-sm-1 wt-pr-sm-2 wt-pt-xs-1 wt-pr-xs-2 wt-nudge-t-3" data-gdpr-toggle-label="" aria-hidden="true">
                        On
                </label>
                <input class="wt-switch wt-switch--small" type="checkbox" name="personalization_consent" id="personalization_consent" checked="" data-gdpr-toggle="" data-checked-label="On" data-unchecked-label="Off">
                <label class="wt-switch__toggle" for="personalization_consent" aria-hidden="true"></label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="wt-pt-xl-6 wt-display-flex-xl wt-pt-lg-6 wt-display-flex-lg wt-pt-md-6 wt-display-flex-md wt-pt-sm-6 wt-display-flex-sm wt-pt-xs-6 wt-display-flex-xs" data-section="third_party_consent">
        <div class="wt-flex-xl-5 wt-flex-lg-5 wt-flex-md-5 wt-flex-sm-5 wt-flex-xs-5">
            <h2 class="wt-text-title-01 wt-mb-xs-4 wt-break-word">Personalized Advertising</h2>
<p class="wt-text-caption wt-mb-xs-2">To enable personalized advertising (like interest-based ads), we may share your data with our marketing and advertising partners using cookies and other technologies. Those partners may have their own information they’ve collected about you. Turning off the personalized advertising setting won’t stop you from seeing Etsy ads, but it may make the ads you see less relevant or more repetitive.</p>
<p class="wt-text-caption wt-mb-xs-2"> Personalized advertising may be considered a “sale” or “sharing” of information under California and other state privacy laws, and you may have a right to opt out. Turning off personalized advertising allows you to exercise your right to opt out. Learn more in our <a class="wt-text-link" href="https://www.etsy.com/legal/privacy/">Privacy Policy.</a>, <a class="wt-text-link" href="https://help.etsy.com/hc/en-us/articles/360042433614-How-to-Opt-out-of-Personalized-Advertising">Help Center</a>, and <a class="wt-text-link" href="https://www.etsy.com/legal/cookies">Cookies &amp; Similar Technologies Policy</a>.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="wt-flex-xl-1 wt-flex-lg-1 wt-flex-md-1 wt-flex-sm-1 wt-flex-xs-1">
            <div class="wt-display-flex-xl wt-display-flex-lg wt-display-flex-md wt-display-flex-sm wt-display-flex-xs wt-nudge-b-4">
                <label for="third_party_consent" class="wt-text-caption wt-pt-xl-1 wt-pr-xl-2 wt-pt-lg-1 wt-pr-lg-2 wt-pt-md-1 wt-pr-md-2 wt-pt-sm-1 wt-pr-sm-2 wt-pt-xs-1 wt-pr-xs-2 wt-nudge-t-3" aria-hidden="true" data-gdpr-toggle-label="">
                        On
                </label>
                <input class="wt-switch wt-switch--small" type="checkbox" name="third_party_consent" id="third_party_consent" checked="" data-gdpr-toggle="" data-checked-label="On" data-unchecked-label="Off">
                <label class="wt-switch__toggle" for="third_party_consent" aria-hidden="true"></label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

class="wt-overlay__main wt-pt-xs-4 wt-pt-md-6"><div class="wt-text-body wt-mb-xs-5"><p class="wt-mb-xs-2">We noticed you're checking in on the weekend. If you already prepare, package, or ship orders on Saturday or Sunday, now you have the option to update the standard Monday–Friday schedule so shoppers will see more accurate, sometimes faster <a class="wt-text-link" target="_blank" href="https://help.etsy.com/hc/articles/360001922768-How-to-Set-Up-Estimated-Delivery-Dates?segment=selling">delivery dates<span class="wt-screen-reader-only">Opens a new tab</span></a>. Etsy shoppers have shown they're more likely to buy items that ship faster—even if it's only by one day!</p><ul><li>Keep in mind, adding Sunday to your schedule means you prepare or package orders that day—but you don't have to ship them. If a <a class="wt-text-link" target="_blank" href="https://help.etsy.com/hc/articles/115015588087-How-to-Set-Processing-Times-and-Ship-By-Dates?segment=selling">ship-by date<span class="wt-screen-reader-only">Opens a new tab</span></a> falls on a Sunday, we'll always bump it to the next business day.</li><li>You can change this setting any time.</li></ul></div><fieldset><legend class="wt-label wt-mb-xs-2">I'd like to add these weekend days to my Monday–Friday schedule</legend><div class="wt-display-inline-flex-md"><div
